column5: Hey Cousin,  Happy Birthday.  I hope you find many reasons to smile... what an awesome day!  Happy birthday to you , happy birthday to you, happy birthday dear Fred.............. Happy birthday to you!!!  Enjoy  Cheers,  Jen
Have a great day Easton!  Happy Birthday...hope you get all the things you want (maybe an all expense paid charter from your cousin??? LOL)
Thanks all! Heading out to the BOQ in a few minutes. Taking my daughter and my father for some R and R, if that includes fishing as relaxation.  Easton
Happy B day Have a good one
Happy happy to you Fred. Have a super trip to the BOQ.
